abuses 
aylwins twohour speech restored a tradition in chile in which 
the president delivers his annual state of the nation address 
before congress 
during pincohets rule congress was suspended and the annual 
address was delivered before military commanders government 
officials and supporters 
the 74yearold general remains commander of the 60000man army 
