by security officials of the pinochet regime but also terrorist 
attacks in which soldiers were the victims 
after taking power in a 1973 coup pinochet launched a harsh 
crackdown on the supporters of the ousted leftist government 
thousands were arrested and many were tortured or killed tens of 
thousands were forced into exile 
