representatives as delegate general it traditionally recognizes 
countries and not governments or movements 
the plos status as a general delegation is the only of its kind 
in france it is less than a full state and does not imply 
diplomatic recognition 
the plo maintains a diplomatic mission in athens and its ranking 
member is accorded the title of head of mission 
